	<body>
		<outline text="June 2021" type="calendarMonth" name="june2021" >
			<outline text="June 14" type="calendarDay" name="14" >
				<outline text="Yes! You can use Obsidian's mobile app to open the Logseq folder. You can also use any other mobile apps that support Markdown or Org mode. https://t.co/tfvqmwN6OV" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:44:05 GMT" tweetId="1404419370986577920" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404419370986577920" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Thank you for the shout out! https://t.co/fLp7D7cMDe" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:40:39 GMT" tweetId="1404418508708974605" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404418508708974605" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Beautiful! We have a publish prototype which is using the JSON export, your devlog looks better! https://t.co/AuKFcsH5qJ" type="tweet" created="Mon, 14 Jun 2021 12:39:28 GMT" tweetId="1404418210263232512" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1404418210263232512" inReplyToId="" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				</outline>
			<outline text="June 12" type="calendarDay" name="12" >
				<outline text="Big fan of OPML, the OPML import is coming soon. https://t.co/67F4PwsbFm" type="tweet" created="Sun, 13 Jun 2021 01:46:39 GMT" tweetId="1403891532617293825" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403891532617293825" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="@djwhitt thank you for your donation 🙏 - Your contribution means a lot to us!
https://t.co/KGsf0HWKvQ" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 20:03:17 GMT" tweetId="1403805121570611200" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403805121570611200" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="0.1.7 is just out! Full changelog at https://t.co/4f6qjMwkBh https://t.co/cz7n2HqS7e" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 12:52:07 GMT" tweetId="1403696615567753218" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403696615567753218" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Thank you for the good words! We're actually looking for some funds to make Logseq better, if anyone is interested in or has recommendations, both DM and replies are welcome, RTs appreciated 🙏 https://t.co/9BW8hOvOIJ" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 07:57:58 GMT" tweetId="1403622590283800581" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403622590283800581" tweetUserName="logseq" />
				<outline text="Interesting! https://t.co/lYvAmkd3kI" type="tweet" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 07:19:20 GMT" tweetId="1403612867090284547" urltweet="https://twitter.com/logseq/status/1403612867090284547" tweetUserName="logseq" />
